a little vague.

00:52:55.860 --> 00:53:00.030
I do believe that we have many
opportunities to take what we

00:53:00.030 --> 00:53:04.060
know about content and what
you, for one, know about

00:53:04.060 --> 00:53:07.710
technology and also about
the community up here.

00:53:07.710 --> 00:53:13.300
And the real excitement is
to say, here we are.

00:53:13.300 --> 00:53:15.560
Here is the effect we
would like to have.

00:53:15.560 --> 00:53:20.480
What are the technological,
financial, pedagogic, and

00:53:20.480 --> 00:53:24.680
educational, generally,
things we can do with

00:53:24.680 --> 00:53:28.410
technology-enabled media that
would actually shift that

00:53:28.410 --> 00:53:30.970
needle and make the
world better?

00:53:30.970 --> 00:53:33.230
Give you one example--

00:53:33.230 --> 00:53:36.290
so , politics you may have
noticed, is completely screwed

00:53:36.290 --> 00:53:37.900
