find that middle?

00:53:58.700 --> 00:54:02.540
How can we help democracy
to flourish and

00:54:02.540 --> 00:54:04.950
thrive using content?

00:54:04.950 --> 00:54:09.770
And what is technology's place
as a partner in doing that?

